        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-10",
        "text": "Thistle and Pine is amazing! Within 5 minutes of talking to Mandie on our first phone call… we knew she was the perfect fit for us. Her humor, passion, and creativity were exactly what we were looking for. You are not only hiring a kind and professional person that you will enjoy spending time with on your wedding day… but also a supremely talented artist who has a one of a kind vision! Our photos are simply amazing and encapsulated the spirit of the day so incredibly. We love the film shots as well… they all came out so timeless and unique. We can’t wait to share these with our friends and family for years to come. By the end, Mandie felt like an old friend. We really enjoyed our experience with Thistle and Pine and highly recommend!!!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2026-05",
        "text": "Hiring Mandie as our photographer was one of the best wedding decisions we made!  Her vision is unique and her photos are stunning; they’re exactly what we could’ve hoped for.  She captured so many big moments and so many little details beautifully, and her photos really are a perfect representation of our day.  We’ve had a ton of fun going through our wedding photos and picking out our favorites, each time finding new ones to love.  Mandie is also so kind and funny and she was a delight to work with; she made us feel so comfortable and at ease.  We’re so happy that she was there to capture our day!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-04",
        "text": "Mandie was the absolute BEST for our wedding photographer last September (belated review)! Working with Mandie felt so effortless and her artistic liberty for photo choices really made the photos unique. She was also very skilled at directing the wedding party/guests to make pictures even better. The film photos have been a big hit among our family and friends as well. I cannot stress enough how great of a choice Mandie is for your wedding photographer! We will for sure be using her for all future photography sessions we choose to do!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2024-04",
        "text": "Mandie is truly the best! Not only are her photos beautiful, but she is a delightful human being and wonderful to work with! She has photographed my family 3 years in a row (and already booked for this year which will be the 4th time we have used her). She makes the photo sessions effortless and can make anyone comfortable in front of the camera, plus she is amazing with my young children! Somehow she always gets great photos of them-even though I swear they are never still. Mandie is magic, and I highly recommend her to anyone in need of a photographer!!!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-06",
        "text": "As two Massachusetts-based, camera-shy people, Thistle and Pine (Mandie) made all the difference! She is relatable, funny, honest, and gave clear direction in our shoots that made posing less intimidating. Her communication from CO was always amazing as well as when we finally met in person to take photos.\n\nOur photos turned out beautiful!! And we got so many compliments—not just on the pictures, but also on how she managed to be everywhere without being intrusive. She truly didn't miss a shot!  She was efficient and informative, all while cracking jokes, when photographing our wedding party. We also hired her to take videos with her camcorder, and the edit she put together was gorgeous!! I have watched it many times over.\n\nWe couldn’t be happier with our experience and would absolutely hire her again!"
      }
